{"tid":490470,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"主機板vs電源 想慳少少買平啲的話揀邊個","createTime":"2017-12-05T16:07:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-07T05:26:42.000Z","uid":143691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"8be9af8e9e55b95c4292874ab2910d48caaf0940","tid":490470,"uid":143691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T16:07:06.000Z","msg":"打算砌機 但係真係真係唔夠錢，唔想再加多少少&hellip; 兩者之間揀邊個買平啲比較好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n打算下星期開始買零件。原本睇中msi b350m mortar，但係後來又見好多人推薦asus嘅tuf b350m，唔明白貴100蚊貴在邊度<br />\n<br />\n願望清單 清幫手睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nMon： viewsonic xg2703-gs 1440p 144hz g sync<br />\n<br />\n1600X (已經有)<br />\nCryoig H7散熱 (已有)<br />\n兩條3000mhz ram(已有，唔記得型號，trident z rgb)<br />\n下面未買<br />\nGalax gtx 1070 ti<br />\nMSI b350m mortar / (定tuf好？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\nCrucial mx300 275gb ssd<br />\n一個1tb嘅hdd<br />\nCorsair RM 550w / antec 500w<br />\nFractal design define mini c<br />\n用住傷殘版Windows先<br />\n<br />\n原本係怕個電源會好嘈 先揀貴啲<br />\n而家唔知道應唔應該改用多啲錢落主機板度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4915a2a303a805fe149a8c3e97ed0e8efd5fc33e","tid":490470,"uid":143691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T16:13:39.000Z","msg":"仲有就 諗住用嚟打機<br />\n暫時係想打Overwatch 遲下手頭鬆啲 再買其他<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n尼爾自動人形聽人評價都唔錯 可能買佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ea2a668a6e9c71dc3633376e3da6035a2058422","tid":490470,"uid":143691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T04:04:14.000Z","msg":"仲可能買rise of the tome raider<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  push"},{"pid":"351cb901065d60cec20fd7f977c063dda33d3835","tid":490470,"uid":18283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T05:57:43.000Z",